  +files/altivec-fix-0.4.0b.diff, libmpeg2-0.4.0b.ebuild:
  Added a patch to fix compilation-errors on PowerPC with Altivec disabled. This
  may happen if the code is being compiled for a G3-processor (-mcpu=G3 or
  -mcpu=750).

